extensionMeta.name: Sheet Navigation & Actions
extensionMeta.description: Sense Sheet Navigation + Actions visualization extension for Qlik Sense.
extensionMeta.author: Stefan Walther

qDef.qDef:
Pick
(
	$(v_Selected_Dimension_Acc_Type)
    
     ,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)}  >}[FA Invoiced Qty])   
	,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)}  >}[FA Invoiced Qty - Revised])
   

)

Pick
(
	$(v_Selected_Dimension_Acc_Type)
    
    ,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Forecast Qty] )   
	,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Forecast Qty - Revised] )   
 

)

Pick
(
	$(v_Selected_Dimension_Acc_Type)
    
     ,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Hits] )    
	,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Hits - Revised] )  
   

)

Pick
(
	$(v_Selected_Dimension_Acc_Type)
    
     ,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Total Count] )   
	,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Total Count - Revised] )     
   

)

Pick
(
	$(v_Selected_Dimension_Acc_Type)
,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Hits] )    /  Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Total Count] )   
,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Hits - Revised] )    /  Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Total Count - Revised] )   

)

Pick
($(v_Selected_Dimension_Acc_Type)
,
Pick
(
	$(v_Selected_Dimension_Unmet)
    
	,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)}  >}[FA Invoiced Qty])   
    ,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Forecast Qty] ) 
    ,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Hits] )   
    ,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Total Count] ) 
    ,(Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Hits] )    /  Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Total Count] ) )*100
       
)
,


Pick
(
	$(v_Selected_Dimension_Unmet)
    
	,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)}  >}[FA Invoiced Qty - Revised])   
    ,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Forecast Qty - Revised] ) 
    ,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Hits - Revised] )   
    ,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Total Count - Revised] ) 
    ,(Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Hits - Revised] )    /  Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Total Count - Revised] ) )*100
       
)




)

Pick
(
	$(v_Selected_Dimension_Acc_Type)
    
,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Hits] )    /  Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Total Count] )   
,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Hits - Revised] )    /  Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Total Count - Revised] )   



)

Pick
(
	$(v_Selected_Dimension_Acc_Type)
,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Hits] )   
,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Hits - Revised] )   

)

Pick
(
	$(v_Selected_Dimension_Acc_Type)
,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Total Count] )   
,Sum({$<  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} >}[FA Total Count - Revised] )   
)
